      "head_commit": {
        "id": "0c7a016c5898e3b18eac23bd277a7ebdd44f904f",
        "tree_id": "5e7a15188104b43ddf86f4ebe65d321b8e4f4fee",
        "message": "feat: 更改皮肤时，自动识别并选中相应模型 (#930)\n\n* refactor(AccountManage): refactor skin operation logic and enhance model detection\n\n- Centralize account skin operations and dialog state within `AccountManageViewModel`\n- Implement automatic skin model detection (Alex vs. Steve) based on transparency in specific pixel ranges\n- Refactor `ChangeSkinDialog` to use a reactive state-driven approach for pending skin/cape changes\n- Improve image utility performance by optimizing pixel color matching and adding bitmap recycling thresholds\n- Simplify intent handling for skin/cape applications by leveraging the active account state in the ViewModel\n- Add a 6-parameter `combine` extension for cleaner Flow state management\n\n* refactor(AccountManage): simplify Microsoft cape application logic\n\n- Refactor `ApplyMicrosoftCape` intent to accept only the `Cape` object\n- Consolidate cape name resolution and reset state detection within the ViewModel\n- Simplify callback signatures in `AccountManageScreen` and `AccountElements`\n- Improve cape application task to handle reset state and local resource string lookups more efficiently\n\n* chore: 将披风状态一并交由 ViewModel 管理\n\n* chore: 账号相关操作应当以精确为主\n\n* chore: 复用已缓存的皮肤，导入过程中使用 ProgressIndicator\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: movte <movtery228@qq.com>",
